1c5772d8c15ac29154ef6608fbec911da94e13a0.query: SELECT id FROM bigweb_pokemon_expansion WHERE code = $1

22559e4621c9045e4590144d1d37e4fd16f039cd.query: UPDATE bigweb_pokemon_printing SET image_downloaded = true WHERE id = $1

2f2b921c851057572720993cd2813a29207c7151.query: SELECT id FROM bigweb_pokemon_expansion WHERE is_sync = $1

3cf82b06e975f3e26da4f644e834777431f756cd.query:
INSERT INTO bigweb_pokemon_expansion(id, name, code, updated_at, item_count)
            VALUES($1, $2, $3, NOW(), $4)
            ON CONFLICT(id)
            DO UPDATE SET name = $2, code = $3, updated_at = NOW(), item_count = $4

4a4b718714751c7e31190c2f11107b6639743c1e.query: UPDATE pokemon_trainer_fetchable_card SET fetched = True WHERE code = $1

5b4f4d2cff49456dfa0dedc56d741308b378ce07.query: UPDATE pokemon_trainer_printing SET rarity = $1 WHERE code = $2

5f9df77fab0259561e778a1e46ba5b40f975dd79.query:
INSERT INTO bigweb_pokemon_printing(id, name, number, rarity, sale_price, expansion_id, remark)
            VALUES($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            ON CONFLICT(id)
            DO UPDATE SET name = $2, number = $3, rarity = $4, sale_price = $5, expansion_id = $6, remark = $7

6d9b87101055ad229d236b25752fd942cb87ef23.query:

            FROM bigweb_pokemon_printing
            WHERE image_downloaded = false

8136c52ef7ae2b79dd0ca591b2dc51ce2ebb8183.query: SELECT code, expansion_code FROM pokemon_trainer_fetchable_card WHERE fetched = False LIMIT 10

90a1c988d1841c9811f39f7f3a024f5b99bccf25.query:
INSERT INTO pokemon_trainer_fetchable_card(code, fetched, expansion_code) VALUES($1, False, $2)
                ON CONFLICT(code)
                DO UPDATE
                    SET code = $1, fetched = False, expansion_code = $2

a8f44e07dfae68e516a84a18fcf75e15844302b3.query:
INSERT INTO pokemon_trainer_printing(code, kind, name, number, expansion_code)
                   VALUES($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
                   ON CONFLICT(code)
                   DO UPDATE
                   SET kind = $2, name = $3, number = $4, expansion_code = $5

ac2f8b342765a14db2632b4e3bba29edd41faa83.query:
SELECT
                bpc.id,
                bpc.name,
                number,
                rarity,
                sale_price,
                bpcs.name cardset_name,
                bpcs.code as cardset_ref,
                expansion_id,
                last_fetched_at,
                remark
            FROM bigweb_pokemon_printing bpc
            LEFT JOIN bigweb_pokemon_expansion bpcs
            ON bpc.expansion_id = bpcs.id

cf51e32f4ea3398544dfd32e058349ad75fbf870.query:
UPDATE bigweb_pokemon_expansion
            SET is_sync = false, updated_at = NOW()
            WHERE id = $1

d91586a91e6794c68b4c08167a7269ea4077e7b9.query:
UPDATE bigweb_pokemon_expansion
            SET is_sync = true, updated_at = NOW()
            WHERE id = $1

e35b140678e8ff59ca3f255ee044172b69475bec.query:
INSERT INTO pokemon_trainer_expansion(id, code, series, name, release_date, updated_at)
              VALUES(gen_random_uuid(), $1, $2, $3, $4, NOW())
              ON CONFLICT(code)
              DO UPDATE SET code = $1, series = $2, name = $3, release_date = $4, updated_at = NOW()
